Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.45,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（天文学会与占卜研究会之共同研究会）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.29,0:00:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「灵魂悲嚎」？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被强大的魔法所束缚而失去自由的那些生命体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在有些情况下能够只让其内心得到救赎  从而逃脱到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被称为「扰灵」的那个现象也算是其中一种
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:15.25,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40.5}（「扰灵」(Poltergeist、ポルターガイスト)：或译「波尔代热斯现象」，德语，意思是「喧闹的鬼魂」\N(poltern意为发出吵闹声的，geist指死者的鬼魂)。神秘学，超自然学，超心理学名词，表现的现象诸如空无一人房间内\N常常听见脚步声、怪叫声；门外有人敲门，打开门又不见其人等。其实就是俗话说的闹鬼。）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们认为那可能是「灵魂悲嚎」结晶化后所形成的物体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.82,0:00:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说被星水晶所束缚的某人的心灵变成了「灵魂悲嚎」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.53,0:00:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后产生出了那些「黑影」吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道是不是由于星水晶的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.61,0:00:35.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过如果认为那是「灵魂悲嚎」的碎片的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么它的主人如今一定是被一个和自己不同的意识所支配着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:43.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要说得让小子你容易理解的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.68,0:00:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就叫做「恶魔附身」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.43,0:00:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「恶魔附身」…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.35,0:00:49.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,失去自我的自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.19,0:00:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么在不释放那个生命体的情况下就没有解决方案
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.86,0:01:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  如果是星水晶的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.35,0:01:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们来说力量根本就无法与之抗衡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.20,0:01:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说  这也是连那个「Thousand Master」都无法使用的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.48,0:01:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之  被盯上的究竟是这座学园
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.39,0:01:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.52,0:01:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,继续去调查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.59,0:01:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.13,0:01:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.19,0:01:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许有奖赏也说不定哦  伊文
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.30,0:01:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想空欢喜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.56,0:01:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊文洁琳！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.66,0:01:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仍然没有得到查明的怪异「黑影」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.49,0:01:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,它和被盗的星水晶究竟有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.89,0:01:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,另外  在其中暗自活动的黑蔷薇男爵的真实身份又是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他究竟是不是涅吉所思念的那个人物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谜团就这样变得越来越深…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.06,0:01:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！过了3分钟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想死一次看看吗喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:33.90,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,「竟然瞒着我去和涅吉老师…？那种事情我绝对不允许！」by 绫香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,by 绫香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.22,0:03:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？涅吉他？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.77,0:03:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  午休的时候我看到他在里面的操场散步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是进行上次那个怪异「黑影」的调查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那也没必要一个人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.38,0:03:49.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难得有我们这些搭档在他左右啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去帮忙～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:03:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  那么大家一起去帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  明日菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…虽然有点麻烦不过也没办法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙也真是  没有我们的话什么都做不成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又把话说得那么拐弯抹角的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.57,0:04:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等  稍等  那边的没品位卓柏T恤军团的各位同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:18.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,班长！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫没品位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,军团？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为你没品位所以我才说你没品位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  莳绘同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯…是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你穿着那种衣服还好意思说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  刹那同学  什么叫「那种衣服」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说这也是涅吉老师哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莳绘你也真愿意跟着班长一起这么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵…  这只不过是受形势使然…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和班长住一个房间啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是够呛啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都给我住嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  另外我有事情想问你们军团的大家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.99,0:04:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想问的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.47,0:04:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,军团？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前几天你们和涅吉老师偷偷摸摸地去野营了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:04.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是做过调查的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,木乃香！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但那是卓柏研究会的野营活动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卓柏研究会的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…所以我才没有收到邀请吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对对！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯…但是涅吉老师和卓柏研究会没关系吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:28.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这个就是…那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  明日菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？啊…嗯…是那个是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个！哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.01,0:05:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全不明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不能认真地给我解释明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不好了  过了3分钟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！面要泡软了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:54.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们快朝面赶去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！你们说的「面」是什么意思啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们话还没说完啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  快给我回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是很可疑啊  果然是有什么内情啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:11.26,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,我活着要做社会的一个齿轮～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:13.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想太多了啦  班长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该只不过是她们成员无意中说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.49,0:06:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后形势使得她们最后决定一起出去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊  莳绘同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫「无意中」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫「形势使得」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为你抱有这样的想法所以你才会那么不行的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果用那么随便的心情看待事物的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就根本不可能看穿其本质的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不行吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对！你很不行！作为佐佐木莳绘是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.32,0:06:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不配做佐佐木莳绘！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打击…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:06:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打击～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用英语说「枪」的话就是…「GUN」！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:02.60,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（枪「ガン」(GUN)和表示「打击」的词语「ガーン」发音很相似）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.68,0:07:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,0分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有异议！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎！怎么会这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没有香蕉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！纸巾的话倒是有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无法评分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,意味不明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:17.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,支离破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:18.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,离奇古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,烧肉套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:22.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,惩恶扬善
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天下太平～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:31.79,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（更衣室）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之  不把野营这件事情完全搞清楚我就放不下心来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你会帮我的吧？莳绘同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:43.08,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（打击）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不配做佐佐木莳绘…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎…真是令人头疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人做麻烦事又违反了我的行为准则…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然现在得有个人给我打下手才好啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是被驯服了的小狗一样真诚…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又像是拉车马一样不知疲倦活力无限…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀～跑了好长时间  真是舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我还能继续跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,于是  放学后…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥  有反应了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就这样子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回去喝茶休息去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…那么再转一圈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.87,0:08:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:31.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到涅吉弟弟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.19,0:08:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绿色的风和下午的茶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来自雾之国的「爱与勇气之亲善大使」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我正是…黑蔷薇男爵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.56,0:08:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们又见面了啊  涅吉·斯普林菲尔德阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蔷薇男爵…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…我说！刺到我了啊  大哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到「黑影」了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,男爵！我有话想问你！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！尾巴！尾巴！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,问题吗？这可是有我能回答的和不能回答的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.23,0:09:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请问吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能回答
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请问下一个问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…那么…你对这个东西有印象吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你有印象吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是条漂亮的手链呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有吧！你有印象吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能回答
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请你回答我！男爵！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  今天我就到此告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！你不是「Thousand Master」纳吉·斯普林菲尔德吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,男爵！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉弟弟…原来把男爵看成是那样的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你忘记了吗  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使男爵真的是你的老爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「恶魔附身」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被魔法所束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许没有原来的记忆了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的  我明白  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:36.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到涅～吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是大姐她们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉  我们是有意见所以来找你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  把重要的搭档丢在一边不管
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:54.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,订立临时契约究竟是为了什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:10:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  开始「黑影」的调查了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么做呢？涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…呃…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:22.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是帮了大忙啊  春奈同学  夕映同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我对图书馆岛里哪里有什么是完全不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.36,0:11:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用不用  反正我们喜欢去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且帮助寻找的不是我们  而是山田呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用我们帮忙真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,摇晃得那么厉害感觉要倒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.17,0:11:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的  是吧？夏美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？啊…嗯…嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,猜拳输掉了也是没办法的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是约定嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是呢  千鹤姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,石头剪子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:11:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:11:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.14,0:12:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈  我赢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎～？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要提那个啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.98,0:12:09.22,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（打击！）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  莳绘？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:16.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就当作没有看见吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  我是你父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:28.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定接受你试试看了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不配做佐佐木莳绘…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打击！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不配做父亲！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,电光石火般地结束啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  班长她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.33,0:12:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  她现在好像在怀疑野营这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法的练习从今往后也要多加小心才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是为了涅吉老师  我们多加小心吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…让你们过于操心了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:12:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:13:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  都这个时候了还说什么话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼头魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀哦呀哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想是谁呢  原来是涅吉小弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…古菲同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.66,0:13:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做得很不错  古菲同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就照这个样子若无其事地  若无其事地套出野营的秘密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…也没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阳光温暖明媚  所以和明日菜同学她们一起散步…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  涅吉小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  有什么事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就若无其事地问一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像你前不久和明日菜她们偷偷摸摸地去野营了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  好像其实背后还有着不可告人的可疑秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想找你问个明白  班长是那么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  若无其事地回答我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看我给你一饭勺！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.84,0:13:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:57.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:13:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这哪里是若无其事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,班…班长同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  哎呀  涅吉老师  贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然说我去寻找什么可疑的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  古菲同学究竟是在想些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讨厌啊  刚才的请忘记了哦  涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就没有点更好的借口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,班长同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,野营没有邀请你去真是很抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  哎呀  不要这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是那个意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:41.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下次去的时候我一定会邀请班长同学的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这次就请原谅我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:49.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您  我会期待的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我才是  做出了失礼的举动  实在对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我先告辞了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:14:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说谎了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  班长同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:06.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔杖有反应了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…班长同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千鹤姐  茶泡好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏美？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又开始了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:44.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:50.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔士的森林…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.11,0:16:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉弟弟！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  大家也到这个世界来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:10.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出来了啊  妖精！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小刹  快抓住那家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,承命！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:35.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是被那个妖精所操纵了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师  发动契约吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时候干脆就一起上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？大姐  那样太乱来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？真的要那么做吗  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搭档  神乐坂明日菜  近卫木乃香  樱咲刹那  宫崎和香  鸣泷风香  鸣泷史伽  长濑枫！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向我展示出来吧  那隐藏的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,契约发动！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:34.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  变身了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是西方侦探和日本侦探啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…在下倒不觉得有什么大变化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,散步部3人组全部都是Cosplay卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,与此相对…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呜…好冷啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这边却全部是失败卡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.27,0:17:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.77,0:17:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快使用你们的从者专用道具啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？我们不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忍！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,Banner;3;0;0,虽然讨厌青蛙但是却又可以毫不在意地变身为青蛙的枫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.39,0:18:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！变身了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枫姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枫姐姐居然变身为青蛙真是太厉害了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  我只是心中默念「如果能变身就好啦～」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枫同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是涅吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉小弟！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,tel ma amorista！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,睡眠之光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快出现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.67,0:18:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着远方的门扉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:18:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向着浓雾的彼端！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,tel ma amorista！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:11.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成功啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.69,0:19:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉  没有感冒吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天我和在伦敦的阿妮亚通电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后啊  她说她寄宿的家庭里的饭菜根本不适合她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还搞得她长出了痘子来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚还说啊  从今往后都要去外面吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,相当生气的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:19:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  还有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今年黑蔷薇也开得很漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我会把照片也附带在信里给你寄来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一个又一个的谜团不断地扰乱着涅吉的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,星水晶  幻想空间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.66,0:20:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  黑蔷薇男爵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,它们最终究竟会引导出什么样的答案呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:23.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,睁大你的眼睛期待下集吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听别人说「天才就是让那99%的汗水付诸东流的1%的灵感」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.18,0:22:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下集是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.18,0:22:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「哦…男爵原来是蔷薇的种类啊。我还以为是薯类呢」by 春奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.30,0:22:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,顺带一提  我的画有99%都是我的灵感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这难道就是超级天才？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.26,0:22:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻帆良战队  笨蛋Ranger 倒A
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.22,0:22:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋战队终于潜入了邪恶组织「恶恶团」的总指挥部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.33,0:22:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.51,0:22:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是黑暗将军「Doctor Pu」所设下的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈  就如你们团队的名称一样果然都是些白痴啊  笨蛋战队
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:31.82,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40.5}（「まぜるなき」：没有任何添加成分，纯天然炸弹）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:31.82,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40.5}（「火気厳禁」：远离火种）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.99,0:22:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就陪伴着一起升天吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.90,0:22:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  你这混蛋「Doctor Pu」！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.52,0:22:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是定时炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.35,0:22:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那要是爆炸的话  我们就都完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.70,0:22:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真像是图画中所描绘的危机时刻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.62,0:22:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.76,0:22:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对那炸弹我们就不能采取什么行动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太远了我们够不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.14,0:22:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  等等  那样的话  我能行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.61,0:22:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,粉红笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用我的丝带把炸弹甩到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.43,0:23:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行不通的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.75,0:23:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是随便触碰到炸弹什么地方的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.67,0:23:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能定时器就会跳过而直接爆炸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.77,0:23:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.79,0:23:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,粉色笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.17,0:23:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.83,0:23:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.98,0:23:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.02,0:23:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.57,0:23:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.87,0:23:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了  笨蛋战队！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.07,0:23:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的英勇身姿我是绝对…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Hige!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:16.85,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,さあチャレンジャー　行け！ばかレンジャー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.09,0:22:20.56,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,走り出せ　魂抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.73,0:22:24.13,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,進め　デンジャー　行け！ばかレンジャー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:28.10,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,駆け抜けろ　世界を dash and go！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.94,0:22:38.10,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,煙渦巻く　大地踏みしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.26,0:22:45.34,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,吹き抜けてゆく　風を抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:52.97,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,友という名の　勇気を纏って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.00,0:23:00.08,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,愛という名の　正義をかざして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:04.65,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Ready Go！Go！　狙い定め
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:12.02,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Ready Ban！Ban！　ひとつになれ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.31,0:23:15.98,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,五つの魂よ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.06,0:23:21.37,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,さあチャレンジャー　行け！ばかレンジャー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.64,0:23:25.63,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,立ち上がれ　今こそ don't give up！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:16.85,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧　Challenger　上啊！笨蛋Ranger
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.09,0:22:20.56,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就出发　守护自己的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.73,0:22:24.13,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,前进吧　Danger　上啊！笨蛋Ranger
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:28.10,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情地奔跑　在世界中 dash and go！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.94,0:22:38.10,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,烟雾环绕　踏过这大地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.26,0:22:45.34,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,任凭吹打　经受住风浪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:52.97,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,以「友谊」的名义　将勇气集结起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.00,0:23:00.08,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,以「爱」的名义　将正义高高举起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:04.65,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Ready Go！Go！　目标锁定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:12.02,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,Ready Ban！Ban！　合而为一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.31,0:23:15.98,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,五个灵魂啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.06,0:23:21.37,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧　Challenger　上啊！笨蛋Ranger
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.64,0:23:25.63,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来　正是现在 don't give up！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:01:58.40,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,（Kuso1：杯面上打着马塞克是什么意思啊…这个是「日清食品」公司生产的一种杯面…上写：「バリカタ」干脆面）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:00.53,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,（Kuso2：「一遍、死んでみるみゃ！」：出自动画「地獄少女」的主人公阎魔爱的名台词「一遍、死んでみる？」）
